{
  "texts": [
    "The DRMM [46], introduced by Guo et al., uses a histogram to map the relevance between the query and words in the document.",
    "proposed Match SRNN [117], which models complex interactions between input texts by using a neural tensor layer.",
    "Xiong et al.",
    "proposed KNRM [18],which uses a kernel pooling layer to calculate the relevance between the query and words in the document.",
    "Dai et al.introduced Conv-KNRM [150], a model for the soft matching of n-grams for ad-hoc IR by using a CNN."
  ]
}